\cf7 \cb3 \strokec7 Hi Logan. It's great to meet you.\cb1 \
\cb3 A decade is a significant amount of time to nurture an idea\'97that kind of sustained engagement suggests something meaningful is taking shape. Art projects that evolve over years often carry a depth that comes from living with them, letting them change alongside you.\cb1 \
\cb3 I'd love to hear about it. What form is the project taking? Are we talking visual art, performance, digital work, or something that blends categories? And what's kept it alive in your mind for so long\'97is there a particular theme, question, or vision that keeps drawing you back to it?\cb1 \
