\cf7 \cb3 \strokec7 That's fascinating, Logan. A drag persona that's been gestating for ten years carries a lot of weight\'97there's something powerful about an artistic identity that evolves alongside you over that kind of timeframe.\cb1 \
\cb3 Drag has such a rich history as both performance art and personal expression, from ballroom culture to mainstream stages. I'm curious about yours:\cb1 \
\cb3 What's the story or concept behind the persona? Is there a character arc, a particular aesthetic, or a message you're exploring through them? And where are you at with it now\'97are you thinking about bringing them to life soon, or still in the development phase?\cb1 \
\cb3 I'd love to hear more about what's drawn you to this project for so long.\cb1 \
