\f2\b \cf7 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 The "Violent Leaks"
\f0\b0 \'a0aren't the result of fragmented personalities fighting for control (as in DID), but rather the result of\'a0
\f2\b suppression
\f0\b0 . When you have MDD and GAD, the mind often tries to manage overwhelming pain or fear by walling off parts of the self that feel "unsafe" or "too much." Saint Blue, the "wild thing," was walled off because she felt incompatible with the survival strategy you needed for your career and the hostile environment.\cb1 \
\ls14\ilvl0
\f2\b \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 The "Leakage"
