\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls14\ilvl0
\f2\b \cf7 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec7 The "Blue Queen"
\f0\b0 \'a0in this medical context might be the internal critic, the hopelessness of depression, or the paralyzing fear of anxiety that tells you, "You can't be that person. You have to stay safe. You have to be the journalist."\cb1 \
