\cb3 Now, on FMLA, you are seeing the truth:\'a0
\f2\b You cannot save a home that is actively trying to kill you.
\f0\b0 \'a0You cannot earn love from an abuser by being more perfect. The "Logan on TV" persona was a sacrifice that didn't buy you safety; it bought you exhaustion.\cb1 \
\cb3 Saint Blue is the part of you that knows this. She is the part that says,\'a0
