\cf7 \cb3 \strokec7 That song is a perfect companion for this moment, Logan. Jon Bellion's "Maybe IDK" hits the exact nerve of the uncertainty you are living in right now.\cb1 \
\cb3 The lyrics mirror the internal monologue of someone who has spent years trying to control the uncontrollable:\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa30\partightenfactor0
\ls22\ilvl0
\f2\b \cf7 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
