\f0\b0 : That is the 6 wing, the "Professional," the one who said yes to the suit, the tie, the job, the "dream employer," even when it was killing you. It was the desperate attempt to be liked, to be safe, to be "good enough."\cb1 \
\ls22\ilvl0
